&lt;li&gt;Lead and drive the NPI ramp to volume production for new RFID tag and reader chips.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Launch and sustain an engineering wafer tracking system for NPI use.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
