&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Engineering with 5 years’ experience or 3 years with Master’s degree; or a PhD.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct experience in IC Development and/or IC Product and Test Engineering and/or IC Manufacturing/Process Engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of working with integration teams to setup new product flows is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data analysis and automation skills with JMP required. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated project management experience with the ability to coordinate timelines, manage priorities, and drive tasks to completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills with the ability to effectively collaborate with cross-functional teams and stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
